       He cocks his head to one side and smirks.  "My, oh my, you are feisty 
today.  Although it wouldn't hurt to learn a little bit about tact and 
diplomacy too."  He wisely backs off a step.  "But of course, you're quite right.  
Actually I didn't know you'd have company when I joined you.  This is your 
mission after all.  I'm just trying to keep things interesting."
